units real
atom_style molecular
boundary p p p 



pair_style lj/cut 5.0
bond_style harmonic
angle_style harmonic



special_bonds lj 0.0 0.0 0.5
read_data input_water_with_topology.txt
include water_utilities.txt



group water type 1 2 
velocity water create 300 48455 mom yes rot yes



fix integrator all nvt temp 300.0 300.0 0.1
thermo_style custom step   temp  press 
thermo 100
timestep 0.0001



run 10000
timestep 1
unfix integrator
fix integrator all nvt temp 300.0 300.0 10


timestep 0.1

dump 1 all custom 100 simulation_data.lammpstrj id type x y z
run 10000
